repos_data.description: WHATWG-compliant and fast URL parser written in modern C++, part of Node.js, Clickhouse, Redpanda, Kong, Telegram and Cloudflare Workers.

Unicode routines (UTF8, UTF16, UTF32) and Base64: billions of characters per second using SSE2, AVX2, NEON, AVX-512, RISC-V Vector Extension, LoongArch64. Part of Node.js, WebKit/Safari, Ladybird, Cloudflare Workers and Bun.
